{"tid":870214,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"夏温拿兔 Havana Rabbit","createTime":"2018-10-21T02:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T03:57:22.000Z","uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"149438b266bab436ac9e490e0021d95b6bdb379d","tid":870214,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErZSyQaNOrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErZSyQaNOrE&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAev755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=066ef421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErZSyQaNOrE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bDf3VF4LHqc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbDf3VF4LHqc&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAev755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d0c32e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bDf3VF4LHqc</a>"},{"pid":"76cf053101d338ccc3085912ec89faf68b6ed538","tid":870214,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>不要同兔仔洗澡! 好危險!</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兔子很愛乾淨，會自動自己清理洗澡。同兔仔洗澡是很危險的，會令牠精神創傷，嚇怕到呆和僵硬，經常這樣會心臟病發死。但是，有一個例外：就是如果牠們有poopy butthole, 可以給牠們一個butt bath, 但不要用手直接拉牠們的糞便，因為會連皮拉出來。要用水浸到牠們的肛門和腳然後就可以慢慢清理。兔仔是被捕獵的動物，在大自然內是每個捕獵者的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 關於洗澡危險 和怎樣給牠們butt bath:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6UcoZHBlQ80&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAev755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=04cb06cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果主人試過幫兔子洗澡，可能見過兔子用後腳站起來，左右手上下方向擦。這時候兔子其實不是同你玩水，這個姿態是代表不高興，想主人不要理會牠。以下video可看到主人給兔子洗澡時，兔子在3:26被嚇暈：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6zkyjfOq36g&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAev755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=09996f97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g</a>"},{"pid":"3bb27972c61dc95a2ca51042b7a87791a5028d3e","tid":870214,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔仔的墊材- 危險不要買！</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要買aromatic phenols：Pine &amp; Cedar Shavings (松木及紅杉木的木屑)，會傷兔子的肝和呼吸系統。其他litter materials 就可以。以下video有解釋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oc51RrXXrmc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOc51RrXXrmc&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAev755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=7f9b1f46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oc51RrXXrmc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">詳細資訊關於Pine＆Cedar Shavings可去:</span> <a href=\"https://rabbit.org/care/shavings.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Fcare%2Fshavings.html&d=0DyZiuH13tzm9JKnqJWAev755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3e3da356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/care/shavings.html</a>"}]}